# Never commit real secrets or per-environment config into the toolkit.
# Templates live in examples/*.example (kept).
*-token
*.env
.kanban-*
# .release-pr.json IS committed (non-secret project config: board id + public API
# base + artifact list) — same as agent-webhook-bridge and kanban-board. It drives
# bin/release-pr-body + bin/promote-released-cards and must be in-repo for the
# release tooling to run reproducibly (incl. CI).
